Citations:
Fundamentals of Computer Graphics, Marschner and Shirley
Ray Tracing in One Weekend by Peter Shirley
Perlin Noise (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perlin_noise)
Ambient Occlusion (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ambient_occlusion)

How to run:
From the Assets directory, run ../RayTracer <lua script> to produce an image with the filename given in the lua script.

Objective list:

1. Supersampling
2. Additional primitives (plane and cylinder)
3. Glossy reflection
4. Refraction
5. Glossy refraction
6. Soft shadow
7. Animation
8. Ambient occlusion
9. Bump mapping
10. Final scene